## Context

One of the core project goals: build a secure and scalable user authentication system.

## Content

- OAuth 2.0 social login support (Google, GitHub)
- JWT-based session management (Access Token + Refresh Token)
- Multi-factor authentication (MFA) option
- Role-based access control (RBAC)

## Rationale

Authentication is the foundation of all services, so it is set as the first milestone.

## Constraints

- PII data must be stored on domestic servers only
- OWASP Top 10 security guidelines compliance

## Open Questions

- SSO (Single Sign-On) integration scope
